OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773831918
OL,3,CJersey Milk recalled after being
OL,4,Ccontaminated with chemicals
OL,6,FCustomers, wholesalers and retailers
OL,7,Fof Jersey Dairy have been issued an
OL,8,Furgent product recall after some of
OL,9,Fits produce has been "contaminated
OL,10,Fwith a chemical unfit for human
OL,11,Fconsumption."
OL,13,FSmall batches of 2.5% fat reduced
OL,14,Fmilk, 1 litre with use by date of
OL,15,FMonday 23 March and 250g unsalted
OL,16,Fbutter with the best before of Monday
OL,17,F8 June 2026 have been found to be
OL,18,Fcontaminated.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
