OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773831918
OL,3,CJersey Milk recalled after being
OL,4,Ccontaminated with chemicals
OL,6,FThe dairy company says: "The level of
OL,7,Fcontamination is very small, estimated
OL,8,Fat 1 part per million, and there have
OL,9,Fbeen no reports of illness at these
OL,10,Flevels, so this recall is a
OL,11,Fprecautionary measure.
OL,13,F"Other Jersey Dairy products are
OL,14,Funaffected."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/3
