OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773831918
OL,3,CJersey Milk recalled after being
OL,4,Ccontaminated with chemicals
OL,6,FThe Environmental Health Department
OL,7,Fand Public Health have been working
OL,8,Fclosely with the firm, and Jersey
OL,9,FDairy says: "We offer our sincere
OL,10,Fapologies to all customers for the
OL,11,Finconvenience caused and appreciate
OL,12,Fyour cooperation in removing these
OL,13,Fproducts from sale and use with
OL,14,Fimmediate effect."
